VABL – PRO/AM Event

VABL – PRO/AM Event

Hooray!

October 5 @ 8:00 am - 5:00 pm

VABL – PRO/AM Event

Get ready for an electrifying night of boxing action at the Melbourne Pavilion on October 5th! The VABL Pro/Amateur Event will bring together the best of both worlds, showcasing elite professional fighters alongside rising amateur stars. This is your chance to witness intense matchups, skillful displays, and the raw passion of the sport as these athletes go head-to-head in the ring. Don’t miss out on what promises to be an unforgettable evening of boxing excellence. Be there to support your favorites and experience the thrill of live boxing at its finest!
